# Custom Resolver instance test
# Tests that users can provide a custom PreRelease.Resolver instance
# Uses a single tag 'v2.5.0-nightly' that requires:
# - Custom Resolver to map 'nightly' to SNAPSHOT

# Initialise with custom tag
> gitInit
> reload

# Custom Resolver should map 'nightly' to SNAPSHOT
> checkCustomResolver

# After commit, Extended should include metadata, Standard should not
$ exec git -C . commit --allow-empty --no-gpg-sign -m "post-release work"
> reload
> checkExtendedShow
